{{bor+|ur|fa-cls|سَلَام}}, itself from {{der|ur|ar|سَلَام}}. {{etydate|c|1503}} as {{inh|ur|hi-mid|سلام}}.<ref>{{R:ur:UDB|w=108140}}</ref>

